{"title_page": "Byst\u0159i\u010dka", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Byst\u0159i\u010dka\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline=Bystricka prehrada.jpg\n|image_caption = [[Byst\u0159i\u010dka Dam]]\n|image_shield=Bystricka_znak.PNG\n|image_flag=Byst\u0159i\u010dka prapor.png\n|image_seal = Bystricka pecet.png\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1=[[Zl\u00edn Region|Zl\u00edn]]\n|subdivision_type2=[[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n|subdivision_name2=[[Vset\u00edn District|Vset\u00edn]]\n|coordinates = {{coord|49|24|56|N|17|58|13|E|region:CZ|display=inline,title}}\n|pushpin_map=Czech Republic|area_total_km2=9.52\n|population_total=941|population_as_of=2005\n|population_density_km2=auto\n|elevation_m=380\n|postal_code_type=Postal&nbsp;code|postal_code=756 24\n|website=http://www.bystricka.cz\n}}\n\n'''Byst\u0159i\u010dka''' ([[Romanian language|Romanian]] ''Bistri\u0163a Morav\u0103'') is a village and municipality (''[[obec]]'') in [[Vset\u00edn District]] in the [[Zl\u00edn Region]] of the Czech Republic.\n\nThe municipality covers an area of {{convert|9.52|km2|sqmi}}, and has a population of 941 (as at 2005).\n\nByst\u0159i\u010dka lies on the [[Vset\u00ednsk\u00e1 Be\u010dva]] river, approximately {{convert|9|km|mi|0}} north of [[Vset\u00edn]], {{convert|30|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} north-east of [[Zl\u00edn]], and {{convert|266|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} east of [[Prague]].\n\n==References==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20090714232845/http://www.czso.cz/lexikon/mos_vdb.nsf/okresy/CZ0723 Czech Statistical Office: Municipalities of Vset\u00edn District]\n\n{{commons category|Byst\u0159i\u010dka}}\n{{Vset\u00edn District}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bystricka}}\n[[Category:Villages in Vset\u00edn District]]\n[[Category:Moravian Wallachia]]\n\n\n{{Zl\u00edn-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n|name=Byst\u0159i\u010dka\n|settlement_type=Municipality\n|image_skyline=Bystricka prehrada.jpg\n|image_caption = [[Byst\u0159i\u010dka Dam]]\n|image_shield=Bystricka_znak.PNG\n|image_flag=Byst\u0159i\u010dka prapor.png\n|image_seal = Bystricka pecet.png\n|subdivision_type=Country\n|subdivision_name={{CZE}}\n|subdivision_type1=[[Regions of the Czech Republic|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1=[[Zl\u00edn Region|Zl\u00edn]]\n|subdivision_type2=[[Districts of the Czech Republic|District]]\n|subdivision_name2=[[Vset\u00edn District|Vset\u00edn]]\n|coordinates = {{coord|49|24|56|N|17|58|13|E|region:CZ|display=inline,title}}\n|pushpin_map=Czech Republic|area_total_km2=9.52\n|population_total=941|population_as_of=2005\n|population_density_km2=auto\n|elevation_m=380\n|postal_code_type=Postal&nbsp;code|postal_code=756 24\n|website=http://www.bystricka.cz\n}}\n\n'''Byst\u0159i\u010dka''' ([[Romanian language|Romanian]] ''Bistri\u0163a Morav\u0103'') is a village and municipality (''[[obec]]'') in [[Vset\u00edn District]] in the [[Zl\u00edn Region]] of the Czech Republic.\n\nThe municipality covers an area of {{convert|9.52|km2|sqmi}}, and has a population of 941 (as at 2005).\n\nByst\u0159i\u010dka lies on the [[Vset\u00ednsk\u00e1 Be\u010dva]] river, approximately {{convert|9|km|mi|0}} north of [[Vset\u00edn]], {{convert|30|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} north-east of [[Zl\u00edn]], and {{convert|266|km|mi|0|abbr=on}} east of [[Prague]].\n\n==References==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20090714232845/http://www.czso.cz/lexikon/mos_vdb.nsf/okresy/CZ0723 Czech Statistical Office: Municipalities of Vset\u00edn District]\n\n{{commons category|Byst\u0159i\u010dka}}\n{{Vset\u00edn District}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bystricka}}\n[[Category:Villages in Vset\u00edn District]]\n[[Category:Moravian Wallachia]]\n\n{{Zl\u00edn-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Byst%C5%99i%C4%8Dka"}
